<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h3>Archive/Container Files Inventory Report</h3>
    <p>Hi there, below are the report on the Filesets Inventory Run (Container/Archive files) that ran and below is the results after
       it has finished running:
    </p>

    <br>

    <% if (@inventory_data.blank?) %>
      <p>No container/inventory files were discover</p>
    <% else %>
      <% @inventory_data.each_with_index do |data, index| %>
        <%= data[index][0] %>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>

    <br><br>
    <p> - Scholars Archive Support </p>
    <p>Email Date & Time: <%= Time.now.strftime("%B %-d, %Y - %l:%M %p") %> </p>
  </body>
</html>